OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBand of rain
OL,6,Feasing off during the evening, Cloud
OL,7,Fbreaking up through the evening with
OL,8,Fclear skies for many overnight,
OL,9,Fallowing temperatures to fall and
OL,10,Ffeeling cold. Winds light but breezy
OL,11,Falong the coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FCold start Sunday, then dry
OL,14,Fwith sunny spells during the morning
OL,15,Fbefore turning cloudier during the
OL,16,Fafternoon. Some further sunny spells
OL,17,Flate on.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
