OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBand
OL,6,Fof rain clears south early Monday,
OL,7,Ffollowed by brighter spells. Further
OL,8,Frain Tuesday lunchtime with showers
OL,9,Ffollowing. Wednesday breezy with
OL,10,Fwidespread heavy showers, possibly
OL,11,Fthundery at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
